    <h2 style="font-weight: 700; margin: 40px auto; padding:0 15px">How Soy Wax is Made</h2>
    <p style=" margin-bottom: 1rem; font-size: 20px;">Soy wax is made by extracting oil from soybeans and then
        hydrogenating it
        to create a solid wax. This
        process gives soy wax its unique qualities such as a lower melting point, clean burning, and excellent
        scent throw.</p>

